detail":"Their 'AI Transformation' + agentic framing is replicable. We already have Xenia + chatbot-core; package a DS2 chatbot/automation product, apply ds2-design, add to the tools catalogue, then the site."},{"title":"Client transparency dashboard","detail":"Their real-time dashboard is a trust lever. Our Agora client portal (internal-ops spec) is the same idea — build + foreground it."},{"title":"Hard-specific, objection-handling marketing","detail":"Adopt their exact-number specificity + a 'vs typical agency' comparison block on our site, in our challenge-first voice."}]}$json$::jsonb, 'analyzed', now()
